replyContent: When a foal grow up have to be taken to new paddock with trailer to free stall for next pregnant mare. When a half barn is full, next paddock in the game is unlocked automatically. replyContent: Thank you, Juniper! Buying and selling horses is part of the horse shows that you can see when you tap the Trophy icon. To sell a horse, choose Compete, then any event, choose the horse to sell and specify its price. To buy a horse, choose Vote, browse the horses that take part in competitions and if the horse is for sale, Buy button will appear.
